[[File:Adamant armour set (lg) equipped.png|thumb|130px|A player with adamant armour equipped.]]
'''Adamant equipment''' are items made from [[Metal#Basic metals|adamantite metal]]. Adamant equipment is stronger than [[mithril equipment]], but weaker than [[rune equipment]]. Adamant items are green-coloured. Adamant armour requires 30 [[Defence]] to wield, weapons require 30 [[Attack]].

==Weapons==
'''Adamant weapons''' require an [[Attack]] level of 30 to wield, except for the adamant cane, which requires 28.

===One-handed melee weapons===
{{Infotable Bonuses|Adamant dagger#(unp)|Adamant axe|Adamant mace|Adamant sword|Adamant longsword|Adamant scimitar|Adamant hasta#(unp)|Adamant warhammer|Adamant battleaxe|Adamant pickaxe|Adamant cane|sort=str|nototals=yes}}

===Two-handed melee weapons===
{{Infotable Bonuses|Adamant claws|Adamant spear#(unp)|Adamant 2h sword|Adamant halberd|sort=str|nototals=yes}}

===Ranged weapons and ammo===
{{Infotable Bonuses|Adamant crossbow|Adamant bolts#Unpoisoned|Adamant arrow#(unp)|Adamant brutal|Adamant dart#(unp)|Adamant javelin#Unpoisoned|Adamant thrownaxe|Adamant knife#(unp)|sort=rstr|nototals=yes}}

==Armour==
'''Adamant armour''' is the third-highest quality [[armour]] in the standard spectrum of metal armours ([[Bronze equipment#Armour|bronze]] to [[Dragon equipment#Armour|dragon]]). Adamant armour requires 30 [[Defence]] to wear.

{{Infotable Bonuses|Adamant med helm|Adamant full helm|Adamant chainbody|Adamant platebody|Adamant platelegs|Adamant plateskirt|Adamant sq shield|Adamant kiteshield|Adamant boots|Adamant gloves|Adamant defender#Normal|sort=dslash|nototals=yes}}

==Other==
Ornamental adamant armour, such as [[Adamant heraldic armour|heraldic]] and [[Adamant trimmed armour|trimmed]], have the same bonuses as standard adamant armour. These can be obtained from the member's only [[Treasure Trails]] minigame. These armour sets are often worn by more wealthy players due to their looks and price.

'''Note:''' Other players '''''cannot''''' trim or bless armour. Players claiming to do so are scammers.

